    "By downloading or using the app **QReative: QR Code Reader**, these terms will automatically apply to you." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "بتنزيل تطبيق **QReative: QR Code Reader** أو استخدامه، تنطبق عليك هذه الشروط تلقائيًا."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Durch das Herunterladen oder Verwenden der App **QReative: QR Code Reader** gelten diese Bedingungen automatisch für Sie."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Al descargar o usar la app **QReative: QR Code Reader**, estos términos se aplicarán automáticamente a ti."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En téléchargeant ou en utilisant l'application **QReative: QR Code Reader**, ces conditions s'appliquent automatiquement à vous."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dengan mengunduh atau menggunakan aplikasi **QReative: QR Code Reader**, ketentuan ini secara otomatis berlaku untuk Anda."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "アプリ **QReative: QR Code Reader** をダウンロードまたは使用すると、これらの規約が自動的に適用されます。"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ao baixar ou usar o app **QReative: QR Code Reader**, estes termos se aplicarão automaticamente a você."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "เมื่อดาวน์โหลดหรือใช้แอป **QReative: QR Code Reader** ข้อกำหนดเหล่านี้จะมีผลกับคุณโดยอัตโนมัติ"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**QReative: QR Code Reader** uygulamasını indirerek veya kullanarak bu koşullar otomatik olarak sizin için geçerli olur."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bằng cách tải xuống hoặc sử dụng ứng dụng **QReative: QR Code Reader**, các điều khoản này sẽ tự động áp dụng cho bạn."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "By using the App, you consent to the processing of your information as set forth in this Privacy Policy." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "باستخدام التطبيق، فإنك توافق على معالجة معلوماتك على النحو المبين في سياسة الخصوصية هذه."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
